---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="FraiseQL Use Cases - Real-World Applications"
  description="Explore how FraiseQL solves problems in regulated industries, e-commerce, analytics, and more."
>
  <div style="padding: 2rem; max-width: 1280px; margin: 0 auto;">
    <h1>📚 Use Cases</h1>
    <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; color: #666;">
      <strong>Real-world scenarios showing how FraiseQL delivers value</strong>
    </p>

    <section style="margin: 3rem 0;">
      <h2>By Industry</h2>
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem; margin: 2rem 0;">
        <div style="padding: 1.5rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 8px;">
          <h3>🏥 Regulated Industries</h3>
          <p>Healthcare, finance, government compliance</p>
          <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 1rem 0;">
            <li>✅ HIPAA compliance</li>
            <li>✅ PCI-DSS deterministic latency</li>
            <li>✅ 100% audit trail</li>
            <li>✅ Field-level encryption</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/use-cases/regulated-industries" style="color: #e63946; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;">
            Read Case Study →
          </a>
        </div>

        <div style="padding: 1.5rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 8px;">
          <h3>🏢 Enterprise SaaS</h3>
          <p>Multi-tenant platforms with RBAC</p>
          <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 1rem 0;">
            <li>✅ Row-level isolation</li>
            <li>✅ Database-per-tenant support</li>
            <li>✅ Role-based access control</li>
            <li>✅ Credential rotation</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/use-cases/enterprise-saas" style="color: #e63946; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;">
            Read Case Study →
          </a>
        </div>

        <div style="padding: 1.5rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 8px;">
          <h3>📊 Analytics & BI</h3>
          <p>Real-time dashboards and data warehousing</p>
          <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 1rem 0;">
            <li>✅ Apache Arrow Flight (25-40% compression)</li>
            <li>✅ Materialized views (2,083× faster)</li>
            <li>✅ Zero-copy streaming</li>
            <li>✅ Data warehouse integration</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/use-cases/analytics" style="color: #e63946; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;">
            Read Case Study →
          </a>
        </div>

        <div style="padding: 1.5rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 8px;">
          <h3>🛒 E-Commerce</h3>
          <p>Complex product relationships and inventory</p>
          <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 1rem 0;">
            <li>✅ Product → Variants → Inventory relationships</li>
            <li>✅ Real-time inventory tracking</li>
            <li>✅ Order transaction atomicity</li>
            <li>✅ 1,100 queries → 1 query optimization</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/use-cases/e-commerce" style="color: #e63946; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;">
            Read Case Study →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section style="margin: 3rem 0;">
      <h2>By Problem Solved</h2>
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem; margin: 2rem 0;">
        <div style="padding: 1.5rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 8px; background: #f9fafb;">
          <h3>⚠️ N+1 Queries</h3>
          <p style="color: #666;">
            How compile-time optimization makes N+1 queries impossible
          </p>
          <p style="margin: 1rem 0; font-size: 0.9rem;">
            <strong>Scale:</strong> 10 users × 50 posts × 10 comments = 100-500× latency difference
          </p>
          <a href="/use-cases/n-plus-one" style="color: #e63946; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;">
            Deep Dive →
          </a>
        </div>

        <div style="padding: 1.5rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 8px; background: #f9fafb;">
          <h3>⚡ Unpredictable Performance</h3>
          <p style="color: #666;">
            How compile-time optimization guarantees deterministic latency
          </p>
          <p style="margin: 1rem 0; font-size: 0.9rem;">
            <strong>Result:</strong> P99 only 33% higher than P50 (vs 400% with interpreted)
          </p>
          <a href="/use-cases/unpredictable-performance" style="color: #e63946; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;">
            Deep Dive →
          </a>
        </div>

        <div style="padding: 1.5rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 8px; background: #f9fafb;">
          <h3>🔒 Scattered Authorization</h3>
          <p style="color: #666;">
            How compile-time RBAC prevents authorization bugs
          </p>
          <p style="margin: 1rem 0; font-size: 0.9rem;">
            <strong>Impact:</strong> Authorization bugs that leak data or allow unauthorized access
          </p>
          <a href="/use-cases/scattered-auth" style="color: #e63946; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;">
            Deep Dive →
          </a>
        </div>

        <div style="padding: 1.5rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 8px; background: #f9fafb;">
          <h3>🔄 Migrating from Hasura</h3>
          <p style="color: #666;">
            Step-by-step migration guide with timeline and ROI
          </p>
          <p style="margin: 1rem 0; font-size: 0.9rem;">
            <strong>Timeline:</strong> 2-4 weeks with 9× ROI payback in year one
          </p>
          <a href="/use-cases/migration-from-hasura" style="color: #e63946; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;">
            Deep Dive →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section style="margin: 3rem 0;">
      <h2>Quick Comparison Table</h2>
      <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 1rem 0;">
        <tr style="background: #f5f3ff;">
          <th style="padding: 1rem; text-align: left; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">Use Case</th>
          <th style="padding: 1rem; text-align: left; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">Key Challenge</th>
          <th style="padding: 1rem; text-align: left; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">FraiseQL Solution</th>
          <th style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">Performance</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;"><strong>Regulated Industries</strong></td>
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">Compliance + performance</td>
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">Compile-time guarantees</td>
          <td style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">1-2ms</td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="background: #fafafa;">
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;"><strong>Enterprise SaaS</strong></td>
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">Multi-tenant isolation</td>
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">Database-per-tenant support</td>
          <td style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">1-2ms</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;"><strong>Analytics</strong></td>
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">Large result sets</td>
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">Arrow Flight + materialized views</td>
          <td style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">40× faster</td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="background: #fafafa;">
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;"><strong>E-Commerce</strong></td>
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">N+1 queries</td>
          <td style="padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">Compiler optimization</td>
          <td style="padding: 1rem; text-align: center; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">100-500×</td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </section>

    <section style="margin: 3rem 0;">
      <h2>More Resources</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/for/developers">For Developers</a> – Getting started and development patterns</li>
        <li><a href="/for/architects">For Architects</a> – Architecture decisions and patterns</li>
        <li><a href="/for/compliance">For Compliance Officers</a> – Audit and compliance setup</li>
        <li><a href="/verification">Verification Registry</a> – All claims backed by proof</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <p style="margin-top: 2rem;">
      <a href="/">← Back to Home</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
